先例。署方曾經於2015年7月推介手機召車應用程式Uber，並稱Uber為乘客提供更多交通選擇，為司機帶來更多機會，希望令城市更加安全和四通八達。不過在Uber被捲入犯法風波後，投資推廣署隨即刪文，並稱「由於Uber 現涉嫌在合法範圍外經營，作為一貫政策投資推廣署已將有關個案在本署的網頁刪除」。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<br />\n分類：香港｜編輯精選｜即時新聞｜發表於2017年9月6日 下午12:54<br />\n請支持我們持續發展，透過PayPal或其他方法贊助我們！<br />\n金額：  PayPal － 更安全、更簡單的網上付款方式！"},{"pid":"3fbdce9ec050f470fc0367617c9275d07afdf4e6","tid":389295,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1df67c8669bb6ec9a6e05e36b71f9ef5749f435","tid":389295,"uid":23180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"打完齋仲養你個和尚過世咩"},{"pid":"885fd3668ad5866b15546a8bd0091ec115b3e5cb","tid":389295,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"用完即棄"},{"pid":"2085c5e778ab4ad116cd7f9f5f65ab0705ba03d0","tid":389295,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"有支那<br />\n冇運行"},{"pid":"dc48ea7c3e7c44ba6fe50fba566f05c944ca7f10","tid":389295,"uid":118022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e605d23692358fe23e4c753151071d4c82965a0b","tid":389295,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"政府好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c168b851752f23315bb6588cf8aa7f0679be7826","tid":389295,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1809cf57968edb02f8d0f1a67e20c